          <title>Amd's Ben Conrad Talks About RDNA 4 Laptops, Or Lack Thereof</title>
          <description><![CDATA[AMD's Ben Conrad was interviewed by Notebookcheck.net about the prospects for RDNA 4 laptops in the future. He replied that their current graphics strategy is focused on the desktop market with RDNA 4, implying that we shouldn't expect anything on the RDNA 4 mobile front in the near future.]]></description>
